<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wander-v">wander <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'wɒndə(r)/    美 /'wɑːndər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>闲逛；徘徊；漫步；离开（正道）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>wander about / over the world
周游世界</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>wander ( through / around ) the street</strong>
在街上游荡</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>走神；胡思乱想：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My mind began to wander. What job would I do?
我开始天马行空地思考，我应该做什么样的工作呢？</p><footer>人教⑤ – 3</footer></div></div>